
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SIT Nagpur | Department of Computer Science</title>
    
    <!-- Google Fonts for Modern Typography -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* --- Design Tokens & Variables --- */
        :root {
            --primary: #0A2540;
            --primary-light: #1A365D;
            --accent: #D4AF37;
            --accent-hover: #F3CD44;
            --text-main: #2D3748;
            --text-muted: #64748B;
            --bg-light: #F8FAFC;
            --card-bg: #FFFFFF;
            --shadow-sm: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            --shadow-md: 0 10px 30px rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.06);
            --radius-lg: 16px;
            --radius-md: 12px;
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        /* --- Base Resets --- */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Premium Header & Navigation --- */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), #FFFFFF, var(--accent));
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        header h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #A0AEC0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
        }

        nav button {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            padding: 20px 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
        }

        nav button:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        nav button.active {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        nav button.active::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* --- Master Layout Container --- */
        .main-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            min-height: 50vh;
        }

        /* --- Views Architecture (Tab Switching) --- */
        .view-section {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease forwards;
        }

        .view-section.active-view {
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(15px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* --- Beautiful Card System --- */
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
        }

        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        /* --- Grid & Department Highlights --- */
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .feature-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .feature-item h4 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        /* --- Action UI Buttons --- */
        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.15);
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-light);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.2);
        }

        /* --- Premium Data Table Styling --- */
        .table-container {
            width: 100%;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            text-align: left;
            background: white;
        }

        th {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        td {
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
        }

        tr:hover td {
            background-color: #F1F5F9;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            background-color: #E2E8F0;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .badge.active-spec {
            background-color: #E0F2FE;
            color: #0369A1;
        }

        /* --- Premium Footer --- */
        footer {
            margin-top: 80px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: #94A3B8;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Premium Master Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>Department of Computer Science</h1>
        <h3>Symbiosis Institute of Technology (SIT), Nagpur</h3>
    </header>

    <!-- Navigation Hub (Handles smooth interface switching) -->
    <nav>
        <button id="nav-home" class="active" onclick="switchView('home')">Overview</button>
        <button id="nav-student" onclick="switchView('student')">Student Information Portal</button>
    </nav>

    <!-- Master Layout Content Wrapper -->
    <main class="main-container">

        <!-- VIEW 1: Department Overview Home -->
        <section id="view-home" class="view-section active-view">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>Welcome to our Department</h2>
                <p>We provide a collaborative, high-fidelity environment built around advanced software development ecosystems, emerging AI frameworks, and rigorous computational principles.</p>
                
                <button class="cta-btn" onclick="switchView('student')">
                    Launch Student Portal &rarr;
                </button>

                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h4>Immersive Infrastructure</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 5px 0 0 0;">High-performance computing core laboratories outfitted with industrial testing suites.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h4>Ecosystem Specialisms</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 5px 0 0 0;">Curated engineering tracks spanning Deep Learning, Cloud Architectures, and Cryptography.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h4>Placement Alliances</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 5px 0 0 0;">Strategic dynamic pathways linked explicitly with global Tier-1 tech enterprises.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

